you are perceiving, sensing,

00:20:58.000 --> 00:21:05.050 align:middle line:84%
responding subjectively,
and there is the key word.

00:21:05.050 --> 00:21:09.200 align:middle line:84%
We have plenty of data to show
that plants perceive, sense,

00:21:09.200 --> 00:21:11.560 align:middle line:84%
respond, so they
definitely do that.

00:21:11.560 --> 00:21:16.840 align:middle line:84%
