I often asked myself is

00:21:16.840 --> 00:21:23.710 align:middle line:84%
can do this in any other
way that is not subjective.

00:21:23.710 --> 00:21:26.200 align:middle line:84%
Because to do it
non subjective, it

00:21:26.200 --> 00:21:29.410 align:middle line:84%
means that you're doing it
objectively, which really means

00:21:29.410 --> 00:21:31.810 align:middle line:84%
that you are an object,
but objects don't feel,

00:21:31.810 --> 00:21:33.997 align:middle line:90%
don't perceive, don't respond.

00:21:33.997 --> 00:21:36.859 align:middle line:90%
[CHATTER]

00:21:36.859 --> 00:21:41.640 align:middle line:90%


00:21:41.640 --> 00:21:43.720 align:middle line:84%
The new lab that
I'm setting up here

00:21:43.720 --> 00:21:48.210 align:middle line:84%
at the University of Sydney,
it's called the BI Lab,

00:21:48.210 --> 00:21:51.750 align:middle line:84%
and it stands for
biological intelligence.

00:21:51.750 --> 00:21:55.890 align:middle line:84%
And really it's my little
smirk to the AI people

00:21:55.890 --> 00:21:57.970 align:middle line:90%
so artificial intelligence.

00:21:57.970 --> 00:22:02.560 align:middle line:90%


00:22:02.560 --> 00:22:06.340 align:middle line:84%
We are comfortable in
considering technology

00:22:06.340 --> 00:22:10.240 align:middle line:84%
as becoming intelligent
and even conscious.

00:22:10.240 --> 00:22:12.790 align:middle line:84%
We talk about robots
as if they are alive,

00:22:12.790 --> 00:22:15.430 align:middle line:84%
and yet we are not prepared
to talk about plants as

00:22:15.430 --> 00:22:17.020 align:middle line:90%
if they are alive.

00:22:17.020 --> 00:22:19.540 align:middle line:84%
It's definitely not
considering the question

00:22:19.540 --> 00:22:22.810 align:middle line:84%
of intelligence or consciousness
for these others worthy

00:22:22.810 --> 00:22:23.860 align:middle line:90%
of discussion.

