00:25:28.240 --> 00:25:32.640 align:middle line:84%
So one of the experiments I did
is testing Pavlovian learning

00:25:32.640 --> 00:25:38.010 align:middle line:84%
in plants, specifically peas,
and it's following pretty much

00:25:38.010 --> 00:25:42.570 align:middle line:84%
the same testing protocol
that we use in animals

00:25:42.570 --> 00:25:47.340 align:middle line:84%
and specifically the Pavlovian
protocol with the dog.

00:25:47.340 --> 00:25:53.280 align:middle line:84%
So in the case of Pavlov, he
used a bell, which was always

00:25:53.280 --> 00:25:57.660 align:middle line:84%
preceding the arrival of
dinner, and in response to that,

00:25:57.660 --> 00:25:59.640 align:middle line:84%
the dog will
salivate because it's

00:25:59.640 --> 00:26:01.950 align:middle line:84%
very excited about
the arrival of dinner.

00:26:01.950 --> 00:26:05.880 align:middle line:84%
But repeating these
long enough or times

00:26:05.880 --> 00:26:10.830 align:middle line:84%
enough, the bell on
his own, even when

00:26:10.830 --> 00:26:16.500 align:middle line:84%
there is no dinner coming,
will make the dog salivate.

00:26:16.500 --> 00:26:22.170 align:middle line:84%
Now plants don't salivate,
and I didn't use a bell.

00:26:22.170 --> 00:26:25.980 align:middle line:84%
But instead of a bell,
I used a little fan.

00:26:25.980 --> 00:26:29.120 align:middle line:90%


00:26:29.120 --> 00:26:35.350 align:middle line:84%
And instead of
dinner, I used light.

00:26:35.350 --> 00:26:41.550 align:middle line:90%


00:26:41.550 --> 00:26:45.570 align:middle line:84%
Now this is actually blue
light because the peas really

00:26:45.570 --> 00:26:47.740 align:middle line:90%
like that.

00:26:47.740 --> 00:26:52.330 align:middle line:84%
And what they do, a blue
light, they go towards it.

00:26:52.330 --> 00:26:53.880 align:middle line:90%
So they bend.

00:26:53.880 --> 00:26:57.090 align:middle line:84%
If you repeat
these enough times,

00:26:57.090 --> 00:26:59.430 align:middle line:84%
in this case for
three days, you will

00:26:59.430 --> 00:27:06.030 align:middle line:84%
find that the fan alone
without the light even arriving

00:27:06.030 --> 00:27:10.350 align:middle line:84%
will make the pea bend
in the right direction.

00:27:10.350 --> 00:27:13.560 align:middle line:84%
The fan didn't mean anything,
but the plant somehow

00:27:13.560 --> 00:27:16.350 align:middle line:84%
has learned the association
between these two,

00:27:16.350 --> 00:27:20.910 align:middle line:84%
and just like the dog, the
pea is passing the test

00:27:20.910 --> 00:27:21.795 align:middle line:90%
with flying colors.

00:27:21.795 --> 00:27:25.080 align:middle line:90%


